name: First release candidate for 2.0.0
body: Initial release candidate for the 2.0.0 series.

name: 1.1 series second technology preview
body:
Contains a lot of improvements and enhancements.

Also fixes:
CVE-2013-4118
CVE-2013-4119

name: 1.1 series first technology preview
body:
New features and enhancements:
- WinPR - Windows Portable Runtime.
- RD Gateway support (RDP security only)
- Multithreaded RemoteFX - uses multiple threads to accelerate
  encoding/decoding
- New command line syntax - a new, simpler command line syntax was added
- Asynchronous handling of graphical updates and input - improves responsiveness
- Improved sound performance (no more choppy sound)
- Support for windows compatible .rdp files to preconfigure sessions
- New and improved keyboard subsystem - removes requirement for keyboard description files
- New clients
  - aFreeRDP on Android
  - iFreeRDP on iOS
  - Native client on OS X
- New servers
  - wfreerdp-server on windows
  - mfreerdp-server on OS X
